    @Unsupported
public final class IdeFindListener
extends IdeListener
implements CommandExecutionListener
    A listener of IdeFindOperation events. This listener creates IdeFindOperationDto data transfer objects and passes them to the Activity Watcher Service to be transferred into the User Activity Client Application for further processing.
